articles.title: Mahoraba ~Heartful Days~ - Episode 24 - Bells
articles.description: Ryushi gets a part-time job at a grocer. Then he trips and falls in front of a truck, causing an accident. He's unhurt, but the shock of hearing about it makes Kozue fall unconscious!

articles.title: Mahoraba ~Heartful Days~ - Episode 22 - Precious...
articles.description: Sayoko's parents try to convince her to part ways with Asami, while elsewhere, the Narutaki-so residents realize how much Sayoko and Asami meant to them. Asami tries to intervene, but it's Sayoko's determination that saves the day.

articles.title: Mahoraba ~Heartful Days~ - Episode 21 - Mother and Daughter
articles.description: A strange girl and a maid arrive at Narutaki-so and take Asami and Sayoko away with them! They take them back to a mansion, where Asami meets Sayoko's father and mother, and finally learns the truth of her mother's past.

articles.title: Mahoraba ~Heartful Days~ - Episode 18 - Meow Meow Meow
articles.description: Kozue finds two kittens wandering around the apartment. When one of them surprises her, Saki takes over! Surprise after surprise leads to all of Kozue's personalities coming out and a chaotic day for Ryushi.

articles.title: Mahoraba ~Heartful Days~ - Episode 13 - The treasure of Narutaki-so
articles.description: Kozue discovers the diary of her great-grandfather in the storage room, and inside it is a treasure map! Everyone works together to solve the clues. But the treasure at the end isn't what any of them were expecting...

articles.title: Mahoraba ~Heartful Days~ - Episode 10 - Sketch
articles.description: Miyabi, the art teacher, assigns a drawing of a person as homework. Ryushi's classmates come to his place to do it, where they use Megumi and Sayoko as models. When Kozue and the other residents get back from shopping, they draw them as well.

articles.title: Mahoraba ~Heartful Days~ - Episode 8 - Shopping
articles.description: Ryushi goes on a shopping trip with Kozue, and Megumi and Tamami sneak out after them. Then Kozue's taken over by Saki in the middle of the department store! After the usual misunderstandings, Ryushi finally sees there's more to Saki than her violent side.

articles.title: Mahoraba ~Heartful Days~ - Episode 4 - Warm and Comfy
articles.description: Ryushi goes to art college for the first time and meets his elegant but terrifying teacher, Miyabi. On the way home, he runs into Kozue and Tamami. They go to the park and encounter a maid, then help her search for her missing stamp card.

articles.title: Mahoraba ~Heartful Days~ - Episode 1 - Welcome to Narutaki-so
articles.description: Ryushi arrives at his new apartment complex, where the landlady is his second cousin, Kozue—who is also in high school. He quickly develops a crush on her, but when she trips and falls on him one day, she suddenly becomes a totally different person!
